</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> 8.1. Definition</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>Когда один query возвращает результаты из нескольких Repos, Portal 
</span><span>вычисляет consensus — степень согласованности концепции между Repos.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> 8.2. v1.0 Consensus Strategy: String Normalization</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>v1.0 использует простое string matching после normalization:</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-pre-wrap leading-[1.7]">def normalize(title: str) -&gt; str:
return title.lower().strip().translate(PUNCT_STRIP)</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-pre-wrap leading-[1.7]">def similar(a: str, b: str) -&gt; bool:
return normalize(a) == normalize(b)</p>
