</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">[</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data content" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">pro2</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">](</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">https://github.com/svend4/pro2</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">)</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data code-snippet code">`.pro2`</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Q6-граф концептов, 64 вершины </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Семантический </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
