</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Быстрый старт</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">```</span><span class="token token code code-language">bash</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(0, 81, 194);">git</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash"> clone https://github.com/svend4/nautilus
