</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Подключить свой репозиторий</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Минимально (Level 0–1, 5 минут):</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Положите </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`nautilus.json`</span><span> в корень вашего репо:
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">```</span><span class="token token code code-language">json</span><span class="token token code">
