</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> 10. Query Flow</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> 10.1. Lifecycle</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> Client вызывает </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`portal.query(q, target_repos=None)`</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> Portal загружает registry (cached)
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> Portal фильтрует адаптеры по </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`target_repos`</span><span> (если задан)
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">4.</span><span> Portal параллельно вызывает </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`adapter.fetch(q)`</span><span> для всех выбранных
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">5.</span><span> Portal собирает </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`results_by_repo: dict[str, list[PortalEntry]]`</span><span>
