</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">8.</span><span> Portal возвращает </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`QueryResult`</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> 10.2. Parallelism</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>Adapter calls SHOULD быть параллельными (через thread pool, async, 
</span><span>или multiprocessing). Это критично для performance при росте числа 
</span><span>Repos.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> 10.3. Error Handling</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>Если adapter падает (exception, timeout), Portal MUST:
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Включить repo в </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`errors`</span><span> список QueryResult
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Продолжить обработку остальных
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Не падать целиком
</span></span><span>
</span><span>Timeout per adapter RECOMMENDED: 5 секунд (было 10 в v1.0, снижено 
</span><span>для лучшего UX).
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> 10.4. Timeout Behavior</span><span>
