</span><span><span></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">```</span><span class="token token code code-language">bash</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(110, 118, 135);"># LOC в Python-коде</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash">
