</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Наша методология: разрешение ручное, через правила 1-5
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> 5.4. Red Team / Blue Team</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span>В security и public policy используется структура </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">red vs blue</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>: 
