</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">1.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Исходные draft ветки</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> (</span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(129, 0, 194);">`claude/*`</span><span>) — как audit trail
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">2.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Merged-to-main с header warning</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> — текущее состояние
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">3.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Финальная консолидированная</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> — после Фазы C
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span>Удалять исходные ветки </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">не следует</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> до завершения Фазы C — они 
