>#</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Nautilus Portal MCP Integration</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>Подключение Nautilus Portal к LLM-клиентам через 
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Model Context Protocol</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> (MCP). Позволяет Claude Desktop, 
