</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Установка</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> 1. Установить MCP SDK</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">```</span><span class="token token code code-language">bash</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash">pip </span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(0, 81, 194);">install</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash"> </span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 0);">'mcp&gt;=1.0.0'</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">```</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>Это единственная внешняя зависимость. Сам portal работает без 
</span><span>внешних библиотек (stdlib only).
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> 2. Проверить, что portal.py работает</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">```</span><span class="token token code code-language">bash</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(179, 74, 0);">cd</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash"> /path/to/nautilus
</span></span><span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash">python portal.py --query </span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 0);">"synthesis"</span><span class="token token code">
