<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Шаг 1 — детекция PII (Personally Identifiable Information).</strong> Adapter <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">AnonymizationAdapter</code> сканирует private документ и находит:</p>
