<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Pattern library — <strong>shared asset community</strong>, не proprietary</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">AI-кураторы — <strong>augmentation of community coordination</strong>, не replacement</li>
