</ul>
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Но ключевое отличие от буквальной MMORPG</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Это <strong>не game</strong>. Это <strong>infrastructure that uses game-like engagement patterns</strong>. Outputs are <strong>real</strong>: real code, real documentation, real research, real legal analysis, real medical translation.</p>
