</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">4.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Contributor fees</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>: explicit zero (0%) platform fees for 
</span></span><span>   contributors in dignity-preserving roles
