</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Commitment 7</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span>: Graceful exit. Contributors can leave at 
