</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Direct specific contributor assignment
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Access contributor private data
