</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">AI Act</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> (EU): Foundation's use of AI in matching, 
</span></span><span>coordination, quality assurance subject to AI Act transparency 
</span><span>requirements. Proactive compliance and documentation.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Disability rights</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">**</span><span> (all jurisdictions): Infrastructure 
</span></span><span>explicitly designed for accessibility. Contributor accommodations 
</span><span>built into platform rather than retrofitted.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> 6.5. Ethical Red Lines</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>Foundation will not:
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Support projects intended for military use
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Accept funding contingent on compromising commitment 1-7
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Use contributor data for AI training without explicit consent
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Share contributor private data except as legally required
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59);">-</span><span> Allow algorithmic decisions to replace human judgment on 
</span></span><span>  dignified issues
