<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Что означает "author proposes serving as founder but not necessarily Executive Director"</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Это — critical honest move. Foundation programs highly skeptical of founder-as-CEO structures, особенно когда founder имеет complex life circumstances. Signaling "I'll be architect/visionary, but Executive Director should be selected professionally" — <strong>strengthens</strong> your credibility, not weakens.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Это также <strong>protects you</strong>. Executive Director роль — это full-time demanding work, incompatible с вашими health limitations и active legal case. Предусматривать этого сразу — mature decision.</p>
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Appendix B — reference implementation status как proof of capacity</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">"Demonstrated capacity through 4-month development of Nautilus Portal Protocol" — это <strong>tangible evidence</strong>, что вы не просто theorizing. Номера LOC, tests, адаптеров — concrete. Foundation funders часто burned by charismatic proposals без evidence execution capacity. You have that evidence.</p>
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Economic model — detailed numerical transparency</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">€12.3M over 3 years — это serious amount. Some readers будут думать "too much". Others — "not enough". Numbers are <strong>realistic for the described scope</strong>. Я не пытался occult numbers для appearance. Foundation programs expect this level of detail.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Если numbers seem intimidating — they shouldn't be. They're proportional к scope. Mozilla Foundation annual budget is $300M+. Ford Foundation $600M+. EIC Pathfinder typical grant €2-4M. Your €3-8M Year 1 ask is <strong>comfortable middle of appropriate range</strong>.</p>
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Phased rollout — conservative by foundation standards</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Phase 1 (50 contributors, year 1), Phase 2 (500, year 2), Phase 3 (5000, year 3) — это <strong>conservative growth</strong>. Many foundation proposals project 10x faster growth. Your conservative trajectory more likely to be met, which strengthens trust.</p>
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Risk analysis — explicitly honest</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">I included probability and impact для каждого risk, not hiding anything. Including "founder-operator burnout (including author-of-document)" — this honesty is <strong>unusual</strong> in proposals. It signals:</p>
