<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Foundation programs <strong>reward</strong> this kind of honest self-assessment over confident claims.</p>
<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">Call for Partnership — multiple stakeholder types</h3>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Я структурировал separately по типам partners (AI companies, foundations, academic, policy, contributors) потому что <strong>each reads document differently</strong>. CEO Anthropic reads это иначе, чем program officer Mozilla Foundation. Document works для <strong>all audiences</strong>, каждый находит свой path.</p>
